Subject: Re: Update on 78 FI with Pertronix not starting

I have just replaced the coil with the Bosch Blue Coil with the ballast
resistor built in. I assume that will lower the current to appropriate
levels for the Pertronix. This is based on Richard Atwell's coil page:
http://www.ratwell.com/technical/BlueCoil.html

Ned

